snippet.title: Gilbert och den Kemystiska ön - Intro
snippet.description:
The intro cinematic from the PC game "Gilbert och den Kemystiska ön"
(English title is "Gilbert and the Chemystical island")

This is one of the games that defines my childhood, and one I still love.
So in an attempt to raise awareness for this criminally underrated game of complete awesomeness I will be uploading some clips and music from it.
If any of you know or have played it, feel free to make requests.

All rights belong to their respective owners etc.
